Install alsa-utils, the sound utilities

Provides low-level ALSO (audio/souund) control and diagnostics tools:

- aplay        → play raw/WAV audio via ALSA (output path validation)
- arecord      → record audio via ALSA (input path validation)
- amixer       → CLI mixer control (set/get volumes, mute/unmute)
- alsactl      → save/restore mixer state (persist across reboots)
- speaker-test → generate test tones (basic channel/speaker verification)
- alsamixer    → interactive TUI mixer (less relevant for headless systems)
- iecset       → control IEC958/SPDIF settings
- alsaloop     → create loopback audio devices (advanced/debug use)
- alsabat      → automated audio testing tool (latency/quality analysis)
